Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.81,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's stage is a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With tables, food, and tricks all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:12.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With the appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of construction going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're building a bypass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, do you really know where we are this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been going in circles for half an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, I'm really hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know. Stop nagging and keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. I'm hungry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought my daughter and someone else with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, darling. Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to buy cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we have customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just change it this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to change it often if I want them to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I can't remove them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be seated at the table in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saki-Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, you weren't here before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now for the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're always so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're extremely sorry, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everything sure is shaking badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they said that the drilling causing all the shaking should be done by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just have to bear with it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, I just want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, we got a big sea bream delivery today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'll just have fried shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since tomorrow's a holiday, are you going swordfish fishing like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll prepare everything tonight so I can depart early tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The salt, the wind, and swordfish fishing. That sounds really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that. I'm always alone on holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that, we have customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! That man in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That big fish is a swordfish, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that-'s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of these pictures were taken by a photographer in our fishing group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, how long have you been swordfish fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has been about 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started back when I lived on Hachijo Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about this picture? Is this Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But somehow, this picture feels different from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture must have been taken by an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well look closely. You'll see that the focus Is on the owner and not the fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These kinds of pictures usually focus on the swordfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, you know a lot about photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I used to dream about being a cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah. Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Have you finished work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what a surprise to see you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Isn't Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad said he didn't drink enough, so he went out alone for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, at least you have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, just what I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The conclusion of "Super Detective".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a detective popular with women in this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must be surrounded by girls right now and having a good time drinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such bad luck, the bar is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, it's closed here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alone inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he told us that he was going to prepare his fishing gear for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd better not bother him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Itoh{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mahjong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence, I'm close by! I'll come join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to buy some bread for tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous at night, let's go back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you here with Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} knows karate, so there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it. Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then. I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I allowed you to go drinking, and it lasted till the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My head hurts, so can you please speak softly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could really go for some good coffee now-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, but it seems like he has been dead for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me Miss, but could you tell me where that vase is usually placed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the top of the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that the vase fell on his head because of the shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And unluckily, at that time, his head took a direct hit from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm one of Hanaoka's close friends. My name's Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept waiting, but he never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he wasn't home either. Reiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I came here to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We always looked forward to going to Hachijo during this season every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A straight, bloodstained line...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mess around with the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I wanted to see if the vase actually fell on Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are traces of blood inside the hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is proof that the vase fell on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look at the flowers from the fallen vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They look withered compared to the other flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was just about to go check that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, these flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...are still fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are some white fragments on the ground. This might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably from the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's neither salt nor sugar, it's highly probable that it's some paint from the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should investigate if it has any connection to Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a thin scratch on the beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the fragments fell from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, now to check the opposite side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window's open...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a similar scratch here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The road work is right outside this window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This might not be an accident after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s murder was made to look like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Saki-Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A vase fell on Shigeru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. Master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They took him to the hospital for a legally ordered autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ordered autopsy? That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name's Wada, I'm a cook at this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Yoshiwaza, a waitress here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, if the cause was a vase that fell, isn't this an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death was caused by a vase falling on his skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's a possibility that someone may have done that on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first. I also thought it was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, after further investigation. I reached a different conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the autopsy, we know that Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died last night between 11pm and 1 am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after asking around. I learned that construction work stopped at 10:30pm due to a machine malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's impossible for the vase to have fallen due to the shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take a moment and look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was left at the construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Entangled in the fork, is a line used in fishing swordfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This string was wrapped around a metal bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer used the string and the metal bar to position the vase directly above Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and made it fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When officer Takagi examined the spare refrigerator, he found a frozen sea bream as well as flower petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means that the murderer placed the fork with the line inside the vase and froze it beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, while Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was preparing his fishing gear, the vase directly above his head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was switched with the frozen one. Using an excuse like the water needed changing, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he tied the line from the beam with the line in the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, the culprit went to the construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and tied the other end of the line from the vase to a metal bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he slowly pushed it down, thus pulling the vase and moving it above Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As time passed, the ice inside the vase melted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sums up the trick behind the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing! He's making deductions without sleeping today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, it's Reiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s job to change the water for the flowers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you suspecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why? Why would I kill Shigeru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an envelope I found in Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A report from a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Reiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s activity records that Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...with Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had a partner in this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who made the necessary preparations at the construction site, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:15:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I accidentally saw you last night when I was passing by the work site.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adultery...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who became a hindrance in her affair, was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all exactly as Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Amazing as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, it was nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How crude. Don't step on chairs with your shoes, fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey look, isn't this scratch similar to the one from the vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} who is witnessing the autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that they found sea bream scales on the victim's head and neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fishing is Kanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s hobby after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that they got stuck on when he caught sea bream on one of his trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is... -
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case. I have to bring the both of you back to the station for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment. Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two are not the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that they made that strange device for the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, by the time the vase had fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer knew of their plan and used it to his own advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For their plan to succeed, Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must sit at that exact spot. It's extremely unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the true murderer chose a more reliable method.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He approached Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from behind and, using the frozen sea bream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hit him on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a simpler and more reliable plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why there were sea bream scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the murderer killed Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he rushed to return the sea bream to the refrigerator and removed the gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is because the murderer had to go somewhere as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,more specifically, to where Ran and Conan were, the video shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right... Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, please show them to the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are rubber gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those gloves were worn by the murderer to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a red lipstick stain on the tip of a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same color as the one Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wore yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I'm the murderer simply because the color of the lipstick is the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you were in a rush to get back, you wanted to remove the glove as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the glove was stuck on and wouldn't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then tried to pull it off by biting down on one of the fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the saliva left on the glove belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can confirm whose it is with a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a man who deserved to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twenty-one years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanaoka was a fisherman living on Hachijou Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, he swore with a girl named Aiko Morimura, to share their future together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hanaoka said that he wanted to study cooking, so he abandoned Aiko and left the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aiko sends him off in silence, not even telling him about her pregnancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aiko waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She gave birth to their child alone, and kept waiting for Hanaoka's return while bringing up her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, after waiting for so long, she died last spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this mean... you're Aiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive him. I just couldn't forgive that awful man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, that picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one next to Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s usual seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that picture have been taken by your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The camera didn't focus on the fish, but rather on Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels like a picture taken by a loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hung that picture in the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that he could always gaze at it. Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The picture reminds him of the memories of Aiko on Hachijou Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the corner of the picture there's a signature that resembles the number "one".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aiko's initials.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morimura Aiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? So what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I should forgive him because he displayed a picture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She suffered all the hardships and died alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he missed her that much, then why was there no contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he even send a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had he done that... Had he done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't try to contact your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no matter what Hanaoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had done in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be other ways to convey your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other ways besides an abominable one like murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pulling! This one feels really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, picture time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, move back a little or the fish won't be in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't move further back, you should move back more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay. Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pose for pictures better than you take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hello and welcome to my restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I was just changing the water in the pots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
